rows.label: qst202609_0010
rows.name: Ten'i, are you safe?

rows.label: qst202609_0020
rows.name: It seems the rampage has subsided...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0030
rows.name:
I want you to shatter
my Core Crystal...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0040
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?!

rows.label: qst202609_0050
rows.name: It should be easy now...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0060
rows.name: I don't want to commit any more sins...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0070
rows.name: Don't say such foolish things.

rows.label: qst202609_0080
rows.name: There's no way we could do that.

rows.label: qst202609_0090
rows.name: I will go berserk again...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0100
rows.name: Next time, it might be in a city...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0110
rows.name: I don't want to hurt anyone anymore...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0120
rows.name:
If you truly care for me...[ML:Dash ]
then here and now...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0130
rows.name: I refuse.

rows.label: qst202609_0140
rows.name: Yes, I cannot accept.

rows.label: qst202609_0150
rows.name: Why...?[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0160
rows.name:
The King said it before, didn't
he? He entrusted you to us.

rows.label: qst202609_0170
rows.name:
I think that meant that
even if you went berserk,

rows.label: qst202609_0180
rows.name: we could stop you.

rows.label: qst202609_0190
rows.name:
That's right. There's no need for
you to worry about going berserk.

rows.label: qst202609_0200
rows.name:
We will stop you, no
matter how many times.

rows.label: qst202609_0210
rows.name:
So don't think that it would be
better if you weren't here.

rows.label: qst202609_0220
rows.name:
You've helped us so much, Ten'i.
It's only natural that we help you.

rows.label: qst202609_0230
rows.name: That's what friends are for, right?

rows.label: qst202609_0240
rows.name: Friends...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202609_0250
rows.name:
You know what that word
means, don't you, Ten'i?

rows.label: qst202609_0260
rows.name: Am I...[ML:Dash ] allowed to be with you?

rows.label: qst202609_0270
rows.name: Of course.

rows.label: qst202609_0280
rows.name: Thank you...[ML:Dash ]
